{"tid":1783172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【推到國際關注】世界銀行要求臺灣國民持有支那護照方可被錄用","createTime":"2019-12-14T14:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T15:48:13.000Z","uid":236171,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"02ab610380a470cf50a4e3938fae78fbe5cff58d","tid":1783172,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"擁有 twitter 用戶嘅手足，請宣揚開去<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BethanyAllenEbr/status/1205511187712090112?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBethanyAllenEbr%2Fstatus%2F1205511187712090112%3Fs%3D20&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=15107c5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBethanyAllenEbr%2Fstatus%2F1205511187712090112%3Fs%3D20&h=a0f1eb3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BethanyAllenEbr/status/1205511187712090112?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>世界銀行要求臺灣國民需持有支那護照方可被錄用</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nAxios 爆料指，世界銀行於今年曾要求其臺灣籍的現役員工及求職者，必須持有中華人民共和國護照，否則將不再被錄用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由於臺灣不允許國民享有「臺支雙重國籍」，政策變相宣告臺灣人必須放棄臺灣國籍方可被世界銀行取錄。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n過往，臺灣並非世界銀行正式成員，但世界銀行一直有僱用臺灣籍員工。<br />\n<br />\n世界銀行高層受訪時表示最近已取消以上政策，並對有人事部員工曾採取不符合機構宗旨的政策表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同場加映，歡迎 retweet 埋：</strong><br />\n<br />\n另有臺灣人表示他的聯合國兒童基金會 (UNICEF) 求職戶口國籍申報一欄，在不被通知下自動由「臺灣」轉為「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/WilliamYang120/status/1205659126669250561?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWilliamYang120%2Fstatus%2F1205659126669250561%3Fs%3D20&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=4a24f915\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWilliamYang120%2Fstatus%2F1205659126669250561%3Fs%3D20&h=3d4f26df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/WilliamYang120/status/1205659126669250561?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"6cd